dation":"none","all_time_high":119.02,"all_time_low":63.5,"long_business_summary":"Athena Global Technologies Limited provides software application development, quality assurance (QA) and testing, and digital transformation solutions and services to enterprises in India and internationally. It operates through Software Services; Real Estate; Online Pharmacy Platform services; Online Trade of Pharmaceuticals Products; Online Education Services; and Leasing Activity segments. The company offers Allegro, that enhances the efficiency of property valuation and appraisal documentation processes; Elevate, which provides various services for auto and mobility industry clients; Genius, a cognitive-AI based conversational bot; Arod, a billing model for sustainable usage of client resources; and Cerebrus, which offers cybersecurity solutions. It also provides IT Services, including skilled IT HCM, web and mobile applications, app modernization, API integrations and workflows, ERP/CRM implementation and maintenance, and QA testing services; Data and AI services, such as data analytics and decision sciences, and AI and ML based insights; and infrastructural management services, comprising L0 and L1 tech support, and network and security operations. In addition, the company offers digitalization of records; OCR technology solutions; governance, risk, and compliance consulting services; voice and non-voice technical support; and business process optimization services. Further, it provides advisory, structuring, and sustainability consulting services. Additionally, the company engages in the sale of flats; and leasing of investment properties. It serves the financial, healthcare, oil, pharmaceutical, retail, business services, education, IT, and government industries. The company exports its services. The company was formerly known as VJIL Consulting Limited and changed its name to Athena Global Technologies Limited in October 2015. Athena Global Technologies Limited was incorporated in 1992 and is headquartered in Hyderabad, India."}}